    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "interesting. i've heard a lot of people in the industry saying these regs are basically just a way to push smaller shops out of the market to favor the bigger corps who can afford the lawyers and equipment. do u think there's any truth to that, or is that just people complaining?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
